---
const approachBg = 'https://www.figma.com/api/mcp/asset/2d0f268b-0a01-444e-90ec-3c04adce8cbe';
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden" id="approach">
  <!-- Background image -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img
      src={approachBg}
      alt=""
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
      loading="lazy"
    />
  </div>

  <!-- Content wrapper -->
  <div class="relative z-10 flex items-stretch min-h-[620px]">
    <!-- Invisible left spacer (~31% width) -->
    <div class="hidden lg:block lg:w-[31%] shrink-0"></div>

    <!-- Orange content block -->
    <div
      class="w-full lg:w-[683px] shrink-0 bg-[#F7931E] px-8 lg:px-16 py-16 lg:py-24 flex flex-col items-center text-center"
    >
      <h2
        class="heading-2 text-black mb-8"
      >
        Our Approach
      </h2>

      <p
        class="body-text text-black max-w-[520px] mb-10"
        style="font-family: var(--font-spartan)"
      >
        Think of us as a collaborative technical partner, not a vendor. Our
        process begins by understanding your brand's fit identity and design
        intent, then developing accurate, balanced patterns that support that
        vision. From there, we validate fit through digital or physical
        sampling, refine where needed, and prepare final assets that are ready
        for production. Throughout development, we ensure smooth communication
        and a clean handoff, so your team can move forward confidently, without
        confusion or rework.
      </p>

      <a href="/about" class="btn-black">
        Our Story
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
